262
00:18:11,922 --> 00:18:14,880
the advantages from the sun but suffer from it.

263
00:18:15,297 --> 00:18:19,297
If we do not go to the extremes then we can do a lot of work.

264
00:18:19,797 --> 00:18:21,380
The main thing which we can learn from the Sun

265
00:18:21,671 --> 00:18:25,214
is Its capacity of giving. It always gives.

266
00:18:26,297 --> 00:18:29,421
It does not take anything but always gives.

267
00:18:30,130 --> 00:18:33,463
Due to this tremendous giving power of the Sun

268
00:18:34,214 --> 00:18:37,047
we can have rain, we can have crops and living beings.

269
00:18:37,505 --> 00:18:39,546
If we did not have the sun then we would not have anything.

270
00:18:40,005 --> 00:18:41,421
It is due to the giving power of love of the Sun only, that

271
00:18:41,922 --> 00:18:44,297
we have been able to reach this state.

272
00:18:44,588 --> 00:18:46,630
Thus what we have to learn from the Sun is that we should

273
00:18:46,922 --> 00:18:48,797
also develop the power of giving.

274
00:18:49,130 --> 00:18:50,922
If we look around us we will find people who will always

275
00:18:51,255 --> 00:18:53,838
think, “How I can save money and keep it for myself?”

276
00:18:54,214 --> 00:18:56,671
Even if I give money for some programs, some people still

277
00:18:56,922 --> 00:18:59,047
think how they can save money from that also.

278
00:18:59,505 --> 00:19:01,922
Even if I have given them some money to spend they always

279
00:19:02,214 --> 00:19:05,380
have a tendency to save money from everything. Why?

280
00:19:05,797 --> 00:19:07,588
Because there is a tendency to hold on to something.

281
00:19:07,838 --> 00:19:09,922
If someone goes to the market and they find that prices

282
00:19:10,214 --> 00:19:11,838
have risen, and if we ask, “Why?” they reply that

283
00:19:12,172 --> 00:19:14,130
“Because the others have increased the prices,

284
00:19:14,379 --> 00:19:15,630
that’s why I also increase the price.”

285
00:19:15,963 --> 00:19:18,297
If the (cost) prices of the commodities are not rising then

286
00:19:18,963 --> 00:19:21,297
why do they raise the (selling) price?

287
00:19:22,047 --> 00:19:25,380
They have always a tendency to suck the energy of others.

288
00:19:25,838 --> 00:19:28,172
Even if I want to make a small ceremony for a festive

289
00:19:28,380 --> 00:19:30,463
occasion, then others tell Me,

290
00:19:40,546 --> 00:19:42,214
“Shri Mataji you will not be able to succeed.”

291
00:19:43,214 --> 00:19:45,797
When I ask, “Why?” the reply is that people are corrupt and

292
00:19:46,172 --> 00:19:48,255
they will eat (grab) money.

293
00:19:48,713 --> 00:19:51,546
As I eat the food they eat money, so maybe we will not get

294
00:19:52,005 --> 00:19:54,380
along together. It is such an absurd thing.

295
00:19:54,713 --> 00:19:56,463
Those who are responsible for the country’s welfare,

296
00:19:56,880 --> 00:19:59,005
those who are the administrators and those on whom the power

297
00:19:59,297 --> 00:20:02,255
has been bestowed by God, even they do not understand that

298
00:20:02,755 --> 00:20:05,797
we have to give.

299
00:20:06,297 --> 00:20:10,380
This quality of giving one has to learn from the Sun:

300
00:20:11,630 --> 00:20:14,421
that we have come (on this earth) to give and not to take.

301
00:20:14,797 --> 00:20:17,130
This complete change from within has to be reached with

302
00:20:17,546 --> 00:20:19,130
an understanding that we have to give and not to take.

303
00:20:19,588 --> 00:20:21,671
We have to have the passion of giving.

304
00:20:22,172 --> 00:20:25,005
It’s as if when a mother knows that “Today my son is coming”

305
00:20:25,255 --> 00:20:26,963
then with passion she thinks, “What can I do for him,

306
00:20:27,255 --> 00:20:30,047
what food can I cook for him?”

307
00:20:30,297 --> 00:20:32,588
This is the passion which a mother has.

308
00:20:32,880 --> 00:20:35,671
Even if she doesn’t have the ingredients, she might borrow

309
00:20:36,047 --> 00:20:38,797
them from the neighbors and prepare some sweets for you.

310
00:20:39,047 --> 00:20:41,546
She always feel that she has not done enough.

311
00:20:41,880 --> 00:20:45,922
Unless and until we have this kind of collective passion

312
00:20:46,172 --> 00:20:48,089
from inside and have this kind of feeling about others,

313
00:20:48,380 --> 00:20:51,546
no country can progress, neither our own nor other countries.

314
00:20:52,047 --> 00:20:54,755
But we always have the urge to take things from others,

315
00:20:55,130 --> 00:20:57,339
to plunder from others, to borrow from others or

316
00:20:57,546 --> 00:20:59,505
to deceive others. Because of this urge our children

317
00:20:59,922 --> 00:21:02,339
will suffer, we will suffer and we will not be able

318
00:21:02,546 --> 00:21:05,505
to achieve anything in this country.

319
00:21:05,963 --> 00:21:09,671
In My in-law’s village (inaudible)…to build a lake.

320
00:21:10,130 --> 00:21:12,546
The government gave them money in thousands for the purpose.

321
00:21:13,047 --> 00:21:14,797
But the lake was never built.

322
00:21:15,089 --> 00:21:17,380
They said that they had dug a hole to make a lake but then

323
00:21:17,671 --> 00:21:20,255
they covered it again since they did not find any water.

324
00:21:20,546 --> 00:21:23,130
But in fact the hole was never dug.

325
00:21:23,379 --> 00:21:25,838
So where did the money go?

326
00:21:26,297 --> 00:21:27,922
They sent it to Switzerland (bank).

327
00:21:27,922 --> 00:21:29,671
So the banks will again borrow from Switzerland and send

328
00:21:30,005 --> 00:21:31,421
the money again to Switzerland.

329
00:21:31,755 --> 00:21:33,421
If the Sun acts in this way then we cannot survive

330
00:21:33,421 --> 00:21:35,214
even for one day.

331
00:21:35,505 --> 00:21:38,755
If he alone eats (consumes) everything, what can we eat?

332
00:21:39,630 --> 00:21:42,005
Today we are celebrating the SANKRANTI.

333
00:21:42,713 --> 00:21:47,463
Sankranti means a sort of Kranti (revolution) by which

334
00:21:47,797 --> 00:21:49,380
we acquire the habit of giving.

335
00:21:50,005 --> 00:21:53,713
Everybody says that we should have the habit of giving

336
00:21:54,255 --> 00:21:57,005
but most of the people believe in donating something

337
00:21:57,421 --> 00:21:59,713
to the priest.

338
00:22:00,880 --> 00:22:03,713
Also, many people preach the art of giving

339
00:22:04,005 --> 00:22:06,047
just to fill their own pockets.

340
00:22:06,588 --> 00:22:08,255
This doesn’t have any meaning.

341
00:22:09,005 --> 00:22:13,255
There is always a question of whom to give and why to give.

342
00:22:13,797 --> 00:22:16,172
In fact, in all liberty and freedom, we should see

343
00:22:16,546 --> 00:22:19,130
for ourselves what we are giving for our country,

344
00:22:19,421 --> 00:22:22,880
for our brothers and sisters and our neighbors.

345
00:22:23,922 --> 00:22:26,963
We should not be selfish, but give with all our heart

346
00:22:27,630 --> 00:22:30,421
so that we get all the joy of giving.

347
00:22:31,379 --> 00:22:34,588
When we give with all our heart, the joy that we get

348
00:22:35,546 --> 00:22:38,963
cannot be compared with any other joy.

349
00:22:39,713 --> 00:22:42,130
If we want to feel this kind of joy only, then we should

350
00:22:42,546 --> 00:22:47,463
celebrate the SANKRANTI today.

351
00:22:48,880 --> 00:22:53,838
Our nature should become like the Sun.

352
00:22:54,922 --> 00:22:58,130
Whatever he is doing, he doesn’t have the feeling that

353
00:22:58,755 --> 00:23:02,379
he is doing something. He is doing everything in AKARMA

354
00:23:03,130 --> 00:23:05,379
(without the feeling of doing anything) and constantly

355
00:23:05,838 --> 00:23:08,963
burning himself and giving you joy, light,

356
00:23:09,380 --> 00:23:14,089
the essence of living, and he nourishes you.

357
00:23:14,421 --> 00:23:17,255
We see the Sun every day and many people do Namaskar also,

358
00:23:17,671 --> 00:23:19,421
but we only do Namaskar without imbibing

359
00:23:19,755 --> 00:23:21,214
his qualities of giving.

360
00:23:21,797 --> 00:23:23,797
I told you a very small thing:

361
00:23:24,255 --> 00:23:26,922
that every Sahaja yogi

362
00:23:27,214 --> 00:23:30,505
should plant a banyan tree in his garden.

363
00:23:30,963 --> 00:23:32,380
Why do we have to take money from the government

364
00:23:32,671 --> 00:23:34,255
for this purpose?

365
00:23:34,671 --> 00:23:35,922
Just to plant a tree and put a fence around that

366
00:23:36,255 --> 00:23:37,963
tree doesn’t need much money.

367
00:23:38,379 --> 00:23:39,671
Even to smoke bidi (tobacco) costs more.

368
00:23:40,089 --> 00:23:42,047
Try to do this small thing so that others should see that

369
00:23:42,047 --> 00:23:43,922
you are at least doing something.

370
00:23:44,588 --> 00:23:46,380
In spite of this we always think how we can get money

371
00:23:46,797 --> 00:23:48,671
from others, how we can plunder others and how we can

372
00:23:49,172 --> 00:23:51,297
save money at others cost.

373
00:23:51,671 --> 00:23:53,880
Because of these tendencies within us,

374
00:23:54,339 --> 00:23:56,755
our country can never progress.

375
00:23:57,339 --> 00:23:59,505
We did not have these tendencies before in people,

376
00:24:00,089 --> 00:24:02,130
in the earlier days.

377
00:24:02,713 --> 00:24:06,089
I can tell you that when I was young I saw people who

378
00:24:06,339 --> 00:24:09,671
believed only in giving and never in taking.

379
00:24:10,339 --> 00:24:13,297
I saw them giving only, they did not like taking.

380
00:24:13,880 --> 00:24:17,421
Even the parents did not like it if the children took

381
00:24:18,047 --> 00:24:20,505
something from others and would tell them to return it.

382
00:24:20,880 --> 00:24:22,588
I still remember in My father’s house they had made

383
00:24:22,588 --> 00:24:24,546
some chairs and also an umbrella, out of silver.

384
00:24:25,005 --> 00:24:28,047
Everybody asked, “Why did you make these out of silver?”

385
00:24:28,630 --> 00:24:30,546
So the reply was, “When we have marriage ceremonies,

386
00:24:30,546 --> 00:24:32,838
instead of borrowing or hiring them,

387
00:24:33,089 --> 00:24:34,630
it would be better that we have them with us once

388
00:24:34,630 --> 00:24:36,588
and for all, because if we had to hire then sometimes

389
00:24:36,880 --> 00:24:38,630
we did not get them in time because the earlier person

390
00:24:38,630 --> 00:24:40,255
who had borrowed had not returned them.

391
00:24:40,505 --> 00:24:41,922
And sometimes these umbrellas were lost because someone

392
00:24:41,922 --> 00:24:43,838
had never returned them and so they got lost.”

393
00:24:44,089 --> 00:24:45,297
So what I wanted to say is that if we have money,

394
00:24:45,755 --> 00:24:47,130
we should invest it into something collective.

395
00:24:47,379 --> 00:24:48,671
If you want to construct a badminton court,

396
00:24:48,671 --> 00:24:51,089
then in that court everybody should be able to come

397
00:24:51,089 --> 00:24:52,546
and play and we should not say that only my children

398
00:24:52,880 --> 00:24:54,463
should play in that court. If somebody buys a car,

399
00:24:54,755 --> 00:24:56,005
we should be able to take all the children to school.

400
00:24:56,421 --> 00:24:58,713
Thus we should buy a big car so that all the children

401
00:24:59,214 --> 00:25:00,671
can be taken to school.

402
00:25:01,255 --> 00:25:02,838
This habit of being collective and being useful

403
00:25:03,130 --> 00:25:05,130
to everybody, one should learn from the Sun.

404
00:25:05,421 --> 00:25:07,379
And today is a special day when we can learn this thing

405
00:25:07,671 --> 00:25:11,089
from the Sun. And we should take a vow that

406
00:25:11,630 --> 00:25:14,713
“I’ll do something which is collective.”

407
00:25:15,380 --> 00:25:17,671
I do not understand how people can eat without caring

408
00:25:18,089 --> 00:25:19,630
for the common public.

409
00:25:20,505 --> 00:25:22,379
You do not even worry about your neighbors and do not

410
00:25:22,755 --> 00:25:24,130
do anything for the common people.

411
00:25:24,755 --> 00:25:27,838
I told you a very small thing is to plant a tree.

412
00:25:28,380 --> 00:25:30,922
We have got so many yogis in Maharashtra,

413
00:25:31,297 --> 00:25:33,671
even if each one plants one tree and looks after it,

414
00:25:34,089 --> 00:25:36,505
this will be certainly helpful to everybody.

415
00:25:36,880 --> 00:25:40,630
Thus I request all of you to do something collective and

416
00:25:41,255 --> 00:25:43,130
it will be useful to everybody.

417
00:25:43,797 --> 00:25:46,421
But one should never think how much will I earn from it

418
00:25:46,755 --> 00:25:48,297
and make money out of it.

419
00:25:48,755 --> 00:25:50,671
It should not happen like the way we give money

420
00:25:51,089 --> 00:25:52,380
to the priest.

421
00:25:53,005 --> 00:25:54,963
One should open his heart and lovingly do something

422
00:25:55,255 --> 00:25:56,963
for the collective and feel the joy out of it.

423
00:25:57,797 --> 00:25:59,755
One should make it a habit.

424
00:26:00,047 --> 00:26:01,922
I do not want to say that others should have

425
00:26:02,380 --> 00:26:04,214
everything for free.

426
00:26:04,588 --> 00:26:06,339
I never said that you do something for free for

427
00:26:06,630 --> 00:26:08,671
the people who have come from abroad.

428
00:26:09,172 --> 00:26:11,630
If you look at them you will see that they have brought

429
00:26:11,630 --> 00:26:16,005
so many things for you from abroad to give you as presents.

430
00:26:16,588 --> 00:26:18,755
Of course I have contributed a lot.

431
00:26:19,172 --> 00:26:21,089
But they have also brought a lot of things of their own.

432
00:26:21,463 --> 00:26:23,255
When I saw the presents here, I thought that they were

433
00:26:23,255 --> 00:26:25,214
the presents which I had bought in Rome for you

434
00:26:25,463 --> 00:26:27,339
but then they told Me that these were the presents

435
00:26:27,755 --> 00:26:29,797
which they bought themselves and they had not

436
00:26:29,797 --> 00:26:32,089
brought My presents.

437
00:26:32,463 --> 00:26:34,546
They felt such a lot of joy to bring so many things

438
00:26:34,838 --> 00:26:36,005
for you.

439
00:26:36,379 --> 00:26:39,047
They do not even know in Italy to whom these presents were

440
00:26:39,297 --> 00:26:41,421
to be given but they do not bother.

441
00:26:41,671 --> 00:26:43,463
They leave it to Me to give them to the Sahaja yogis

442
00:26:43,838 --> 00:26:45,505
here in India.

443
00:26:45,880 --> 00:26:48,130
But in India we have a tendency to think only about

444
00:26:48,463 --> 00:26:50,838
our children and about our mother.

445
00:26:51,214 --> 00:26:53,339
Then the mother comes walking, limping on one leg.

446
00:26:53,671 --> 00:26:56,130
Then you start saying that “My mother did not get

447
00:26:56,130 --> 00:26:58,214
a high quality sari.”

448
00:26:58,588 --> 00:27:01,963
Since I do not have one I give her a simple sari.

449
00:27:02,339 --> 00:27:04,880
This is the tendency here.

450
00:27:05,214 --> 00:27:07,505
But with the people from abroad it is just the opposite.

451
00:27:07,797 --> 00:27:09,922
When they came here they came with so many presents

452
00:27:09,922 --> 00:27:13,089
it seems they brought two tons of presents from abroad.

453
00:27:13,421 --> 00:27:15,546
Even My hands starting paining while giving these

454
00:27:15,922 --> 00:27:17,797
two tons of presents.

455
00:27:18,172 --> 00:27:21,047
What I want to say is that they do not expect anything

456
00:27:21,463 --> 00:27:23,339
from you. But your behavior should be such as to show

457
00:27:23,546 --> 00:27:25,963
an example for them. And you should show them that

458
00:27:25,963 --> 00:27:28,380
you are in no way inferior to them,

459
00:27:28,797 --> 00:27:30,838
“We are here really to serve you, to welcome you,

460
00:27:31,172 --> 00:27:32,463
whatever is possible from our side

461
00:27:32,463 --> 00:27:34,380
we do not hesitate to do.”

462
00:27:34,713 --> 00:27:36,421
It doesn’t cost any money nor any hard work.

463
00:27:36,880 --> 00:27:39,297
The only thing is that we should change our outlook.

464
00:27:39,630 --> 00:27:42,214
If even after coming in Sahaja Yoga we are not able

465
00:27:42,214 --> 00:27:44,089
to change our nature in this manner then I do not feel

466
00:27:44,089 --> 00:27:46,713
that we can change the entire humanity with Sahaja Yoga.

467
00:27:46,963 --> 00:27:48,963
The biggest quality in us is to give to others.

468
00:27:49,463 --> 00:27:51,463
And this quality we should imbibe within us.

469
00:27:51,463 --> 00:27:53,421
In Sahaja yoga your Kundalini is awakened and you

470
00:27:53,880 --> 00:27:55,630
realize your spirit but the essence of spirit is like that

471
00:27:56,172 --> 00:27:58,005
of the Sun and this essence is of giving.

472
00:27:58,421 --> 00:28:01,005
If you have seen one photograph of Mine, there is the Sun

473
00:28:01,255 --> 00:28:02,963
shining on My heart; in fact there is a Sun in My heart

474
00:28:03,255 --> 00:28:05,588
and because of this I never feel that I should take something

475
00:28:05,880 --> 00:28:08,380
from them or to plunder anybody.

476
00:28:09,255 --> 00:28:11,505
I do not understand from which part of your head this idea

477
00:28:12,047 --> 00:28:13,588
of plundering them comes from.

478
00:28:14,005 --> 00:28:16,546
This is a very strange behavior.

479
00:28:16,963 --> 00:28:18,755
Sahaja yogis should not think in this way but on the contrary

480
00:28:19,005 --> 00:28:21,047
every day we must think what we can give or do for others.

481
00:28:21,463 --> 00:28:23,339
In Rahuri itself I have started an organization

482
00:28:23,588 --> 00:28:25,172
whose name is “SAHAJ STREE SUDHAR” or “SAMAJSUDHAR”

483
00:28:25,546 --> 00:28:27,089
(association for the welfare of women).

484
00:28:27,505 --> 00:28:29,379
Through Life Eternal Trust we cannot use the money for

485
00:28:29,713 --> 00:28:31,172
the welfare of the women thus we had to create

486
00:28:31,546 --> 00:28:32,755
this organization.

487
00:28:33,047 --> 00:28:34,922
This organization has been registered and people from Canada

488
00:28:35,255 --> 00:28:37,463
and elsewhere are ready to donate to it but here I do not

489
00:28:37,838 --> 00:28:39,505
find anybody to work for this organization.

490
00:28:40,005 --> 00:28:42,463
If the local women take it upon themselves to work for this

491
00:28:42,713 --> 00:28:44,755
organization only then it will succeed.

492
00:28:45,047 --> 00:28:46,922
We have acquired land and all the facilities but we do not

493
00:28:47,297 --> 00:28:49,588
find time to devote for this organization.

494
00:28:50,214 --> 00:28:51,797
So how can we go to this place?

495
00:28:51,797 --> 00:28:53,588
But one should remember that people are coming from abroad

496
00:28:53,588 --> 00:28:55,505
with the money to donate for your organization.

497
00:28:55,755 --> 00:28:57,130
They have brought fourteen machines for the women here.

498
00:28:57,922 --> 00:29:00,005
You can see women loitering about without doing anything.

499
00:29:00,463 --> 00:29:02,255
You can ask them to work so that they can earn

500
00:29:02,255 --> 00:29:04,963
something out of it. And they can prosper.

501
00:29:04,963 --> 00:29:07,421
At least these things we should try to think about.

502
00:29:07,797 --> 00:29:09,421
Instead of that we always think about ourselves.

503
00:29:09,671 --> 00:29:11,255
So the persons who are in Sahaja Yoga should know that this

504
00:29:11,588 --> 00:29:13,339
selfish attitude is not accepted in Sahaja Yoga.

505
00:29:14,089 --> 00:29:15,963
We should think in terms of global advantage.

506
00:29:16,255 --> 00:29:18,172
The lives (Vibhouti) of saint are for the salvation

507
00:29:18,172 --> 00:29:19,838
of the world. And also for the salvation of saint lives,

508
00:29:20,172 --> 00:29:21,380
this world exists.

509
00:29:21,797 --> 00:29:23,880
Thus the saints will be blessed by this attitude…

510
00:29:24,255 --> 00:29:27,421
(VIBHOUTI means Ashes with which Shiva is decorated).

511
00:29:27,963 --> 00:29:31,255
Now you have become saints you should behave like saints

512
00:29:31,588 --> 00:29:33,797
and the first quality of a saint is giving.

513
00:29:33,797 --> 00:29:37,130
You have never heard of a saint plundering anybody.

514
00:29:37,630 --> 00:29:40,922
If a saint thinks of cheating he does not remain a saint.

515
00:29:41,297 --> 00:29:43,172
Thus from our side we should always think how much

516
00:29:43,380 --> 00:29:45,172
we can give and what we can give,

517
00:29:45,421 --> 00:29:49,838
how much love we can give.

518
00:29:50,214 --> 00:29:51,797
And how many people we can help.

519
00:29:52,255 --> 00:29:53,922
All our attention should be for this purpose.

520
00:29:54,797 --> 00:29:56,588
Nowadays there are welfare associations

521
00:29:57,047 --> 00:29:59,421
just for election purposes.

522
00:29:59,838 --> 00:30:02,797
We should not create any such type of welfare association.

523
00:30:03,339 --> 00:30:04,588
But we should create associations in which we can

524
00:30:04,963 --> 00:30:06,880
work selflessly and our love should be NIRVAJYA (selfless)

525
00:30:07,379 --> 00:30:09,880
and we should not expect anything in return.

526
00:30:10,214 --> 00:30:12,463
And there are no limits for our love, it is an endless love.

527
00:30:12,838 --> 00:30:14,922
When we have this kind of love automatically

528
00:30:15,379 --> 00:30:17,214
we will know what is to be done.

529
00:30:17,214 --> 00:30:18,963
The improvements should be done gradually and every

530
00:30:20,380 --> 00:30:22,797
Sahaja yogi should contribute to this collective welfare.

531
00:30:22,797 --> 00:30:24,005
We should try to devote our time for this purpose and

532
00:30:24,297 --> 00:30:26,047
work hard to achieve our goals. It should not happen

533
00:30:26,463 --> 00:30:28,797
that “Shri Mataji has come, She gives a talk,

534
00:30:28,797 --> 00:30:30,922
and when She goes everything is finished.”

535
00:30:30,922 --> 00:30:32,922
These people (from abroad) have done a lot.

536
00:30:32,922 --> 00:30:35,379
They have started schools and social welfare.

537
00:30:35,880 --> 00:30:37,505
We should also start something in this manner.

538
00:30:37,880 --> 00:30:39,755
Sahaja Yoga should not become an association of people

539
00:30:40,297 --> 00:30:42,379
who have realized the spirit and are swimming in the joy

540
00:30:42,379 --> 00:30:45,380
but are lazy lumps.

541
00:30:45,880 --> 00:30:49,089
It should not happen this way.

542
00:30:49,089 --> 00:30:52,339
We should try to see how we can help others.

543
00:30:52,339 --> 00:30:55,255
We should open our eyes to look around us with love

544
00:30:55,255 --> 00:30:57,588
and try to see how we can help others.

545
00:30:58,047 --> 00:31:02,214
Still I have not been able to move to India.

546
00:31:02,588 --> 00:31:04,671
Once I come back to India you will see that

547
00:31:04,963 --> 00:31:07,214
I will make everyone work.

548
00:31:07,214 --> 00:31:09,339
Thus it is advisable to start working before I come.

549
00:31:09,339 --> 00:31:11,838
Sahaja Yoga is not meant only for sitting and meditating.

550
00:31:11,838 --> 00:31:13,713
For meditating why do you need Sahaja Yoga?

551
00:31:14,172 --> 00:31:15,713
You can go the Himalayas.

552
00:31:16,089 --> 00:31:17,797
If you want to stay here and be in Sahaja Yoga then

553
00:31:18,047 --> 00:31:20,089
the common people should be helped by Sahaja Yoga.

554
00:31:20,588 --> 00:31:22,671
But Sahaja Yoga should not become like these

555
00:31:22,671 --> 00:31:24,505
modern welfare organizations.

556
00:31:25,380 --> 00:31:27,214
We should try to achieve our goals with full sincerity

557
00:31:27,505 --> 00:31:29,797
and only then we can say that we have established Sahaja Yoga.

558
00:31:30,880 --> 00:31:33,713
Now I heard a lot of praise for Me.

559
00:31:34,255 --> 00:31:37,089
I heard the songs and they gave Me a lot of Joy and

560
00:31:37,463 --> 00:31:40,047
satisfaction that people have recognized Me.

561
00:31:40,880 --> 00:31:42,963
But you should remember one thing – you should work

562
00:31:43,214 --> 00:31:44,838
in order to know yourself because you cannot see

563
00:31:45,130 --> 00:31:46,797
yourself in the mirror.

564
00:31:47,214 --> 00:31:49,255
You should be able to see what you have achieved,

565
00:31:49,880 --> 00:31:51,379
like in the earlier days you used to look after

566
00:31:51,797 --> 00:31:53,755
your household, your children. In the same manner,

567
00:31:54,005 --> 00:31:56,339
if you are not able to work for the collective,

568
00:31:56,339 --> 00:31:58,505
then in My opinion, you have not achieved anything

569
00:31:58,797 --> 00:32:00,797
through Sahaja Yoga.

570
00:32:01,047 --> 00:32:03,089
You have remained where you were,

571
00:32:03,421 --> 00:32:05,380
you have not progressed at all.

572
00:32:05,880 --> 00:32:09,838
Next year when I come, you should be able to tell Me

573
00:32:10,297 --> 00:32:12,379
how many banyan trees you have planted.

574
00:32:12,922 --> 00:32:16,421
Secondly, you should be able to tell Me what collective

575
00:32:16,880 --> 00:32:18,546
or social work you have done.

576
00:32:19,005 --> 00:32:21,130
If you try to look around you will definitely be able

577
00:32:21,546 --> 00:32:23,671
to see some collective work which you can do

578
00:32:24,089 --> 00:32:25,922
and you should do.

579
00:32:26,963 --> 00:32:28,505
I’m sure you will be able to do it very well.

580
00:32:28,922 --> 00:32:30,797
It doesn’t need any money – only you have to decide

581
00:32:31,339 --> 00:32:32,755
within your heart. When I started Sahaja Yoga,

582
00:32:33,172 --> 00:32:34,713
at that time I’d given realization to one lady only

583
00:32:35,172 --> 00:32:37,005
and I started without any money.

584
00:32:37,630 --> 00:32:39,671
I did not have support from anybody but even then

585
00:32:40,005 --> 00:32:41,797
I started Sahaja Yoga.

586
00:32:42,339 --> 00:32:45,380
But because of honesty of the work and the consistency,

587
00:32:45,797 --> 00:32:47,797
it has spread so much.

588
00:32:48,172 --> 00:32:49,297
Now each one of you, man or woman,

589
00:32:49,963 --> 00:32:52,379
you have the responsibility that when you will

590
00:32:52,630 --> 00:32:56,172
introduce Sahaja Yoga to the general public,

591
00:32:56,880 --> 00:32:59,630
you will be able to give them some proof of the general

592
00:32:59,880 --> 00:33:03,214
well being. You need not break any law for this.

593
00:33:03,505 --> 00:33:05,880
You need not do anything wrong nor need you do

594
00:33:06,172 --> 00:33:09,047
anything unlawful. In a very simple way if you just

595
00:33:09,421 --> 00:33:11,713
open your eyes you will be able to see what you can do

596
00:33:12,130 --> 00:33:13,797
for the general welfare of the people,

597
00:33:13,797 --> 00:33:16,130
how you can help the wellbeing of the people.

598
00:33:16,671 --> 00:33:18,630
And I’m here to give you all the strength and energy

599
00:33:19,005 --> 00:33:20,546
to do this work.

600
00:33:20,880 --> 00:33:22,797
We do not need any vote nor any money or anything else.

601
00:33:23,172 --> 00:33:24,755
You should give you Me a promise that without expecting

602
00:33:25,047 --> 00:33:27,005
anything in return you will start working for

603
00:33:27,005 --> 00:33:29,880
the welfare of the people.

604
00:33:30,255 --> 00:33:32,380
Sometimes, it might so happen that when people start

605
00:33:32,380 --> 00:33:35,005
some welfare work they go round asking for funds.

606
00:33:35,005 --> 00:33:37,005
This is wrong. We should not ask for money in the beginning.

607
00:33:37,005 --> 00:33:39,630
First you should start some work which does not need money.

608
00:33:39,922 --> 00:33:41,880
Everyone feels that without money we cannot do anything.

609
00:33:41,880 --> 00:33:44,172
You have got the powers so why do you need money?

610
00:33:44,546 --> 00:33:47,838
If somebody is sick or not well in your neighborhood

611
00:33:48,214 --> 00:33:52,005
then you can go and visit him and try to soothe that person.

612
00:33:53,713 --> 00:33:54,922
Instead of that, what I see is that

613
00:33:55,297 --> 00:33:56,713
you bring the sick person to Me.

614
00:33:57,089 --> 00:33:58,421
The other day, someone brought

615
00:33:58,421 --> 00:34:00,214
an injured person to Me. He had a broken arm.

616
00:34:00,463 --> 00:34:02,214
A Sahaja yogi could have treated him in two minutes and

617
00:34:02,421 --> 00:34:04,214
made him well but instead of that, they brought him to Me

618
00:34:04,505 --> 00:34:05,713
and that too right in the middle of a public program

619
00:34:06,005 --> 00:34:07,505
and asked Me to treat his arm.

620
00:34:07,838 --> 00:34:09,172
You are so many and all the powers are flowing

621
00:34:09,505 --> 00:34:11,463
through your hands but still you do not use them.

622
00:34:11,797 --> 00:34:15,505
If you are not able to treat even these small ailments

623
00:34:16,297 --> 00:34:20,379
what is the use of you being a Sahaja yogi? Someone says,

624
00:34:21,214 --> 00:34:23,880
"my mother is sick, my father has broken his leg.”

625
00:34:24,797 --> 00:34:29,005
Instead of bringing them to Me you can easily treat them.

626
00:34:29,421 --> 00:34:32,463
You do have the powers, try to use them.

627
00:34:33,089 --> 00:34:35,130
Thus you should be able to help the people without

628
00:34:36,047 --> 00:34:39,214
expecting anything in return and with full Joy.

629
00:34:39,797 --> 00:34:42,505
You will be able to feel a lot of joy when you have

630
00:34:43,047 --> 00:34:45,630
the feeling that you do not do anything but you are just

631
00:34:48,047 --> 00:34:50,963
an instrument of God and you are living in this world,

632
00:34:52,089 --> 00:34:55,379
in this country and you are giving something special to them.

633
00:34:56,005 --> 00:34:58,463
It is such a big thing, such a big understanding.

634
00:34:58,713 --> 00:35:00,339
With such a feeling, if all of you decide to work,

635
00:35:00,755 --> 00:35:03,755
then, you will be able to do something for others

636
00:35:04,421 --> 00:35:07,546
and other people will see what Sahaja Yoga is.

637
00:35:09,880 --> 00:35:11,379
Now people think what is Sahaja Yoga –

638
00:35:11,922 --> 00:35:14,421
just everybody meditating together and that’s all.

639
00:35:14,880 --> 00:35:17,172
Even if there is some problem in the country Sahaja yogis

640
00:35:17,421 --> 00:35:19,546
are just sitting in meditation.

641
00:35:19,922 --> 00:35:21,797
One man came and told Me, “My wife doesn’t cook.”

642
00:35:21,797 --> 00:35:23,838
I asked, “Why?” He said, “She just meditates.”

643
00:35:24,255 --> 00:35:26,005
So I said, “Is it so? But who told her that?”

644
00:35:26,255 --> 00:35:28,339
First she should cook, for meditation even

645
00:35:28,588 --> 00:35:30,546
five minutes are sufficient.

646
00:35:30,797 --> 00:35:33,047
I have given you the power and the energy to cook well.

647
00:35:33,047 --> 00:35:36,130
Thus one should have the confidence

648
00:35:37,713 --> 00:35:41,047
that you are capable of work.

649
00:35:41,546 --> 00:35:43,546
I am giving you the powers, you can assimilate them.

650
00:35:43,838 --> 00:35:46,047
If you just meditate every day it is not sufficient.

651
00:35:46,047 --> 00:35:48,379
You have to see what wellbeing you are

652
00:35:48,838 --> 00:35:52,380
giving to the others.

653
00:35:53,089 --> 00:35:55,130
But instead of that, you always think about your own wellbeing

654
00:35:55,379 --> 00:35:57,047
and come and ask Me to treat your son, your father,

655
00:35:57,047 --> 00:35:58,838
your mother, or ask that you should get a good job.

656
00:35:59,089 --> 00:36:00,255
And you want that I should also come to your house

657
00:36:00,505 --> 00:36:01,421
to eat, do this, do that.

658
00:36:01,630 --> 00:36:03,630
This way, you try to impose your will upon Me

659
00:36:03,838 --> 00:36:07,421
but about you, what can you do?

660
00:36:07,880 --> 00:36:10,546
You should always remember that you have to do something.

661
00:36:10,838 --> 00:36:12,505
“I will show Shri Mataji what I’m capable of,

662
00:36:12,922 --> 00:36:14,630
to do something special.”

663
00:36:15,005 --> 00:36:18,089
We should decide this once and for all.

664
00:36:18,546 --> 00:36:23,546
I have an image in front of My eyes as Shri Gyaneshwara

665
00:36:23,963 --> 00:36:30,047
has said, "BOLTE PIYUSHANCHE SAGAR."

666
00:36:32,880 --> 00:36:36,588
(Words or sayings are like the oceans of nectar)

667
00:36:37,421 --> 00:36:40,297
Where is it? I want to see it.

668
00:36:41,797 --> 00:36:44,379
Thus on this auspicious day I give you

669
00:36:44,880 --> 00:36:46,630
all My sweet blessings that you will help everyone

670
00:36:47,379 --> 00:36:49,546
and look after their wellbeing and you will treat

671
00:36:49,880 --> 00:36:53,505
everyone with love and you will talk sweetly,

672
00:36:54,047 --> 00:36:56,838
full of love.

673
00:37:21,089 --> 00:37:22,713
He is saying you should put your hands

674
00:37:23,297 --> 00:37:26,130
like this to say that you are bound by Mother's words.

675
00:37:26,630 --> 00:37:29,380
And we will try to do good to others and

676
00:37:29,755 --> 00:37:33,047
we will be very kind to each other.

677
00:37:37,463 --> 00:37:41,671
I've been telling them that we have to be collective

678
00:37:42,214 --> 00:37:44,463
not among only Sahaja Yogis but with others also.

679
00:37:44,838 --> 00:37:47,089
We should see surroundings, what's wrong where,

680
00:37:47,505 --> 00:37:52,713
how we can help. We have many social obligations

681
00:37:53,089 --> 00:37:54,838
which we have to fulfill.

682
00:37:55,214 --> 00:37:57,963
Now you have reached the stage where you can do that

683
00:37:58,339 --> 00:38:03,922
without forming any social organization which collects money

684
00:38:04,339 --> 00:38:06,838
and have saints and things that kind of a nonsense.

685
00:38:07,297 --> 00:38:11,255
But you can see around yourself who are the needy,

686
00:38:11,588 --> 00:38:13,797
to whom you can help.

687
00:38:14,214 --> 00:38:16,339
And that is how you can really give

688
00:38:16,713 --> 00:38:20,380
a very positive form to Sahaja Yoga.

