00:48:23,339 --> 00:48:26,463
I'll be giving this water to all of you

692
00:48:27,089 --> 00:48:32,339
all the leaders and aslo..

693
00:48:33,880 --> 00:48:34,922
you can take it.

694
00:48:35,755 --> 00:48:37,214
this water is very good for

695
00:48:37,671 --> 00:48:42,546
all diseases of the Mooladhara chakra.

